title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Challenges can turn you into a stronger person who others admire. However, you might begin to doubt yourself if you think too hard about lifes setbacks and disappointments now. But remember, you possessed the fortitude to push forward despite the difficulties you encountered. Acknowledging your persistence is an important lesson to learn as taskmaster Saturn moves direct in your 12th House of Inner Peace. Dont get lost in the thicket of your past when the future is right in front of you. Journalist David Brinkley wrote, A successful person is one who can lay a firm foundation with the bricks others have thrown at them. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
